snippet.title: Trials Evolution -  Launch Trailer [UK]
snippet.description:
Time to take Trials HD to the next level. Meet Trials Evolution!                                 The new Xbox LIVE hit is now available! Get ready for the blast of the year!             
• Solo & Multiplayer mode
• Bike & rider customizations
• Full-featured track editor                     
More info on:                           
http://trials.ubi.com/trials-evolution/en-GB/home/
